 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73a8406740558095d211dd84530f3c1a20d658e","tid":1447882,"uid":283080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"機場要繼續！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2431ee85dc42e1f3f290dc732cd8c003bc1cdf","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:53.000Z","msg":"1點去機場"},{"pid":"1e98cfc4a2c8b26e1cfe6e1b77145787a61c9a8f","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"1點機場見"},{"pid":"98979f9ae21379c21c467269c87980e3892039d8","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:14.000Z","msg":"帶齊gear"},{"pid":"46af6681705fec7f0069341b48f757f4cdf2fbd4","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"一齊留意周圍有無鬼"},{"pid":"33db7375c866762dd9c9d6065f7be69f6e421559","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"黑社會！"},{"pid":"376cd3e9709b11d501da57921aeac52af43e9c6b","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"一齊推！"},{"pid":"50ee9a3d89ab2128dfc26653caa4aba50aa5b877","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:25.000Z","msg":"全民去機場"},{"pid":"3a54e1ce26bde5a901f6da1f5fe125580ce1c469","tid":1447882,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77dZi0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77dZi0D.jpg&h=fefe4073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ec19d76f7aa1826b0ea5b5f1f439cdab32e5543","tid":1447882,"uid":261430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYcWmxa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYcWmxa.png&h=d5d77534&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c38cf6e027d880a38852a279d98db3470c5fb89d","tid":1447882,"uid":35091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"77f48a76998fedaef0f9c889a45de2b5a5e4659b","tid":1447882,"uid":61655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"812 去和平接機, 回元氣.<br />\n<br />\n而816 先罷, 要夠多人, 要傷就要真係影響到經濟.<br />\n<br />\n𦇓續罷!!! 香港打工仔都好支持, 人工永遠加得小, 野就愈做愈多. <br />\n<br />\n吸取上次經驗<br />\n<br />\n1. 星期五最好, 因為星期一好多人因為星期日夜出太累. <br />\n2. 有上次經驗, 好多公司都係返半日, 大多提早收工唔係搭唔到車返屋企, 所以有啲公司已經唔洗建議員工返工, 而留在家中.<br />\n3. 要罷就要早啲起身, 攞地鐵早乘優惠.<br />\n4. 地鐵唔好塞死一個站, 係䌓忙轉車點係咁上落搭來回車. <br />\n5. 路面繼續慢駛, 迴旋處行唔到直線<br />\n6. 提早出門去自由行地點鳩烏<br />\n7. 要去機場接朋友"},{"pid":"0e66bf6b107eaea62a43335b696d421f24bc7963","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"塞爆佢！"},{"pid":"f4a924ee0e5316a65262ba9073fbbb788072a4de","tid":1447882,"uid":35091,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7b7887de0849e1825642ae48006fde0a8ae19dd","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>嚴禁衝禁區</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"唔好再撚講底線。"},{"pid":"89061ebcaf26c34c50ea412c322f677d64539028","tid":1447882,"uid":163900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8fa0800d7e95c6a3679db4d32a56df1f995caa0a","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"塞機場！"},{"pid":"6152a1264a3934d7cd66218ae87d6f1664e6e3ca","tid":1447882,"uid":298061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30