br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"504aad0d876feb70e7bf94a96e9484c223b8fc3f","tid":1447882,"uid":193371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"812"},{"pid":"901887ad1ed1114bded2989ff91fd3d81517a34d","tid":1447882,"uid":96540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9323a3fc321646d6a5d2eb2bb7666b14c486cdfd","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"一齊去機場"},{"pid":"3cc366b6e36dd508cbebceb32d28b078309e2e37","tid":1447882,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=7d897b1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=a6b29657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"d11aa7b747f2dee79db3dd77039c62c35657ae73","tid":1447882,"uid":239265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"機場見"},{"pid":"b0ed9d9760c0da4aded4ce41daa2eb73c244fcda","tid":1447882,"uid":251148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:4